’Ů@b25894415f68ff9b754a27aa58cc26ae2fd3ec544971ec2a97a6be0da4ac58eeŮâTitle: title: mkdir
Path: Examples
Content:
Make a directory named foo.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> mkdir foo


```
Make multiple directories and show the paths created.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> mkdir -v foo/bar foo2


```
